This paper deals with analyzing the performance of models on challenge datasets, which is a common problem in natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
